            "custom_liquid": "<style>\n    .about-us-content {\n        max-width: 80vw;\n        text-align: center;\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        align-items: center;\n        margin-inline: auto;\n        color: black;\n        margin-bottom: 40px;\n    }\n    .about-us-desc {\n        margin-bottom: 40px;\n    }\n    .pamela-signature {\n        width: max(14vw,140px);\n    }\n</style>\n<div class=\"about-us-content\">\n    <div class=\"about-us-desc\">\n        <p>Being a pharmacist with 20 years of experience in community and hospital settings, I know how important affordable care is besides safety and effectiveness. When I stumbled upon Proxylane, an incredibly powerful anti-aging molecule, I knew I had to share it with the world.</p>\n    \n        <p>In the skincare industry where aesthetic packaging often overshadows the importance of ingredients, I felt compelled to provide a transparent alternative, allowing consumers to know exactly what they’re paying for—active ingredients and their concentrations, substantiated with analytical lab reports, just like the standards required for medication.</p>\n    \n        <p>With growing demand for safe and clean cosmetics, and many products making organic claims, it’s even more important for pharmacists to put our expertise into ensuring products we use on our face and skin are free from harmful impurities like dioxane and perfluoroalkyl substances, which are often unregulated.</p>\n    \n        <p>This is why X’Factor was created—to infuse our commitment to quality into our products, helping you rediscover your radiance with confidence and peace of mind.</p>\n    </div>\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0724/8062/0716/files/pamela-signature.jpg?v=1767506089\" alt=\"\" class=\"pamela-signature\">\n    <p>\n        <b>\n            Founder of X’Factor,<br>\n            Pamela Quah<br>\n            (RPh. 2644)\n        </b>\n    </p>\n</div>"
